    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "This vehicle represents the pinnacle of automotive preservation. Meticulously maintained and presented in showroom state, it offers an unrivaled driving experience for the discerning collector. Every surface and mechanical component reflects a standard of care rarely seen on the secondary market. We invite you to acquire an investment-grade masterpiece that demands no apologies.",
