      "description": "Hey there! You seriously have to see this beauty in person. It\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy, and I\u2019ve kept it in such incredible shape\u2014it honestly looks and drives like it just rolled off the lot! No scratches, no spills, just pure perfection inside and out. I'm looking for a new home for it where it'll be just as loved as I've loved it. Let's get you behind the wheel for a test drive!",
