    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_14_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_14",
      "description": "Offered is a concours-level E46 M3, featuring the legendary S54B32 power plant. This high-revving inline-six utilizes individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing to deliver linear power up to its 8,000 RPM redline. The chassis is impeccably preserved, with documented subframe reinforcement and a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission. The factory limited-slip differential provides exceptional torque vectoring, while the suspension retains its original damping profile with zero bushing deflection. Mechanically flawless, this example boasts factory-spec compression across all cylinders and a leak-free undercarriage. A true purist\u2019s specimen in showroom condition.",
